When I first tried GPT3 I remember thinking writing as a skill was basically over. Now I think the opposite is true. LLMs still can‚Äôt write, everybody else‚Äôs abilities are atrophying, and being able to clearly express yourself in prose seems like it will only get more valuable

a really crazy experience for me was when i realized most people can't think of second order effects unconsciously, their reasoning just stops after one cause+effect in their head unless they sit down and force it to continue. when i realized this so much of the world made sense
